      "content": "it's not just a \"mistake\" though. it's like... everything i touch just breaks. i look at them and i just feel this heavy guilt. i feel like a burden. i honestly think if i wasn't constantly failing them, they'd actually have a chance at a real, happy life. i'm just a shadow over them.",
